### Health
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Readiness
GET http://localhost:5000/ready

### Create short link
POST http://localhost:5000/api/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUrl": "https://nextjs.org/docs",
  "customCode": "next-docs",
  "title": "Next.js Docs",
  "description": "Official documentation for Next.js",
  "tags": ["docs", "nextjs"]
}

### Public metadata
GET http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs

### Owner summary
GET http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs/admin
X-Admin-Key: replace-with-admin-key-from-create-response

### Update metadata
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: replace-with-admin-key-from-create-response

{
  "title": "Next.js Documentation",
  "tags": ["docs", "react", "nextjs"]
}

### Disable link
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: replace-with-admin-key-from-create-response

{
  "status": "DISABLED"
}

### Reactivate link
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: replace-with-admin-key-from-create-response

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Analytics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs/analytics?limit=25
X-Admin-Key: replace-with-admin-key-from-create-response

### Analytics CSV export
GET http://localhost:5000/api/links/next-docs/analytics/export.csv?limit=1000
X-Admin-Key: replace-with-admin-key-from-create-response

### Redirect
GET http://localhost:5000/next-docs
